  dialogue:
  - 'Stella! My friend, where are you off to in such a rush? '
  - 'Lucien! Something is wrong, the castle staff are behaving wildly aggressively. '
  - "Oh, come now, I\u2019m sure it\u2019s a misunderstanding. Sit and talk with
    me a while. "
  - 'No, I must go to the Earth Kingdom, Hazel needs my help. '
  - 'It need not concern you. Stay and study with me. '
  - "I think I\u2019d better stop by just to check on her. "
  - "Stella\u2026 I\u2019m afraid I can\u2019t let you leave. "
  - Then we have no choice but to fight!
